{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"672691d991","title":"在广州市机关物资疏散情况报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"931a2114b6","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"672691d991"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"f7579cbf81","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"993f360509","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央华南分局1950年12月7日就广州市机关物资疏散情况向中南局并中央作了报告。12月12日，中央根据毛泽东的批语电示华南分局并告中南局及各中央局，指出：中央关于防空疏散的一切指示，均注明是预备性质，自前不向人民公开发动，只限于在党委常委中讨论。现时广州所进行的防空疏散工作已超越预备范围，必须立即纠正，并迅速将自前工作中心转到抗美援期、剩、肃特、土改、练兵及海防方面。"}],"contents":[{"id":"788f2c9496","type":"title","text":"在广州市机关物资疏散情况报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991"},{"id":"f7579cbf81","type":"paragraph","text":"周：广州这样做，似不妥，请去电指示","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991"},{"id":"993f360509","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991"},{"id":"6aa0bbeefb","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991"}],"page":{"id":"029f60cca3","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"672691d991","start":440,"end":440}}}},"__N_SSG":true}